item.description: Java & 文章 Vue.js is an MIT-licensed open source project. It’s an independent project with its ongoing development made possible entirely thanks to the support by these awesome backers. If you’d like to join them, please consider: Become a backer or sponsor on Patreon. Become a backer or sponsor on OpenCollective. One-time donation via PayPal or crypto-currencies. What’s the difference between Patreon and OpenCollective? Funds donated via Patreon go directly to support Evan You’s full-time work on Vue.
